data.description: Honey, Stop the Car! Over 3,000 living SF Huge 6 bedroom / 4 full bath in highly sought-after Stonebridge Subdivision! Upon entrance is the combined Formal living and Dining rooms with fireplace followed by the eat in kitchen with newer stainless-steel appliances and walk in pantry + laundry. One bedroom and full bath also located on the MAIN LEVEL. Head upstairs to the oversized master bedroom with sitting area, bathroom with double vanity and WICS! Second level also offers 4 additional guest bedrooms all with walk-in closets and 2 additional full baths! Upgrades include but not limited to Roof (2022), Furnace (2021), Floors (2021), Fence (2019). There is a crawlspace for extra storage! Beach Park Grade Schools (Zion Benton Township High School) Close proximity to Starbucks, Shopping, and Entertainment, Easy interstate access and so much more! Don't wait, schedule your private showing TODAY!
